description: Get detail data for a linked repository.

parameters.name: name
parameters.description: The repository name, for example myrepos/myrepo.

nested_items.name: repository
nested_items.description: The repository link's detail data that's returned by Proton.

nested_items.name: arn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the linked repository.

nested_items.name: connectionArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of your AWS CodeStar connection that connects Proton to your repository provider account.

nested_items.name: encryptionKey
nested_items.description: Your customer Amazon Web Services KMS encryption key.
